## Implementation steps (TDD order)

```
1. Write failing tests FIRST (RED)
2. Implement minimum to make tests pass (GREEN)
3. Refactor for clarity (IMPROVE)
4. Run full workspace test suite — green
5. Run parallel reviewer agents (code-reviewer + security-reviewer)
6. Fix CRITICAL/HIGH in-commit
7. SSH-signed single coherent commit
8. Push + open DRAFT PR with base=master
9. Parent agent dispatches consistency-reviewer (if part of parallel batch) + decides merge timing
```

